                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1">
                        <locus target="#107r">Fol. 107r: </locus>
                        <desc>Cross.</desc>An elaborate talismanic picture of the cross is drawn
                        over the entire fol. in black, red and yellow.</decoNote>
